Class WorkHoursDialog

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.scene.control.Dialog
      • Routines.WorkHoursDialog
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.event.EventTarget, javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class WorkHoursDialog
extends javafx.scene.control.Dialog
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    The Java class to accompany a GUI constructed in FXML. Basically this take the data from a WorkHours object and sets it up to be displayed nicely on the screen for a user.
